### 获取分组列表
GET http://{{domain}}/admin/auth.group/index
Batoken: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 添加分组
POST http://{{domain}}/admin/auth.group/add
Batoken: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

